### Project Structure

Our Next.js projects follow a specific structure with Hono for API routes and MongoDB/Prisma for database operations:
Directory Structure

src/app/ - Next.js App Router pages and layouts
src/app/api/[[...route]]/ - API routes using Hono
src/components/ - UI components (shadcn/nyxbui)
src/lib/ - Utilities and shared logic
src/store/ - State management
prisma/ - Database schema and migrations

API Organization
Controllers: src/app/api/[[...route]]/controllers/
Middleware: src/app/api/[[...route]]/middleware/
Routes: src/app/api/[[...route]]/routes/
Schemas: src/app/api/[[...route]]/schemas/
Utils: src/app/api/[[...route]]/utils/

